Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.78,0:00:07.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi, you've received an invitation\Nfrom the Schuberstein Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.66,0:00:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's in Germany...\N You're finally going overseas!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.33,0:00:14.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Maihou Competition's around the\Nsame time, but let's cancel that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.38,0:00:18.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Takayanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.30,0:00:21.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be going to Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.80,0:00:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.18,0:00:25.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to enter the\NMaihou Music Competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.30,0:00:29.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But why? They\Ninvited you, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.43,0:00:31.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a golden opportunity\Nthat almost never comes up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.52,0:00:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you also need to get overseas\Nexposure before the Chopin competition!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.31,0:00:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You already won Maihou last year,\Nso there's no reason to make it a priority...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.61,0:00:44.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there is a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.87,0:00:48.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Kousei Arima might be competing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You keep saying that, and\Nhow long have we waited?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.91,0:00:54.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he hasn't shown his face in\Npublic for two whole years now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.67,0:00:56.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are even rumors that\Nhe can't hear anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He might be competing this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.09,0:01:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.38,0:01:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.51,0:01:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But my goal isn't to go overseas,\Nor to play in the Chopin competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.43,0:01:15.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My goal is Kousei Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.77,0:01:19.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The competition that he'll be playing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.75,0:03:05.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's gonna be all right. You\Ncan do this. You can play it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I like your expression.\NDon't get overeager, Takeshi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.51,0:03:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All right, that's\Na great start.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.51,0:03:53.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Takeshi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.64,0:04:00.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she listening to another\Nperson's performance?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.44,0:04:01.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What an intrepid soul!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.28,0:04:11.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.28,0:04:17.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you watching?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are you listening?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.70,0:04:20.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Arima?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.75,0:04:23.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Could this be the same piano?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.67,0:04:26.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He sounds totally different\Nthan everyone before him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.50,0:04:29.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Confronting the music with sincerity...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A strong will enabling him\Nto stand up to his fears.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.18,0:04:36.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An unswerving fortitude at his core.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.18,0:04:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Aiza's Chopin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:47.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm grateful to Arima-kun.\NHe's the one who made him grow up.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.77,0:04:49.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just by existing...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...you pushed the pianist,\NTakeshi Aiza to the top.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.32,0:04:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The reason I was able to hang in there\Nduring the two years you were gone...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.95,0:05:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...was because I always believed\Nthat you'd be back one day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.33,0:05:06.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Have I caught up to you yet?\NOr am I even further behind?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.67,0:05:09.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you let me chase you\Ndown like a mirage again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.13,0:05:13.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you be the one\NI aspire to be?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.38,0:05:17.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hey, answer me. Show\Nme what you've got!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.51,0:05:20.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, now it's your turn.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.81,0:05:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kousei Arima!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh! Well, I gotta\Nadmit he's pretty cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.68,0:06:01.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.72,0:06:03.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome, awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.85,0:06:04.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! He looked this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.64,0:06:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.02,0:06:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.00,0:06:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's the TAKESHI Brigade!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.94,0:06:15.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A rival is a special thing.\NAll the more so for adolescent boys.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.74,0:06:20.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A rival can make you grow far\Nfaster than being taught by someone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.54,0:06:26.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.12,0:06:32.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was you who made Takeshi\Nreach those heights, Kousei Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.63,0:06:37.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was all for the sake\Nof catching up to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:39.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what the piano is saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.72,0:06:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you feel that way, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.81,0:06:45.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:00.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.70,0:07:01.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was great.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:03.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.00,0:07:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Now they start trembling!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.71,0:07:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Did you see that, Arima?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.05,0:07:24.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:28.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, that was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.35,0:07:32.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Creepy...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.90,0:07:35.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There will now be a\N15-minute intermission.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:38.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will resume judging at :45.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.44,0:07:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was really cool, wasn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.45,0:07:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was really tight!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aiza-kun sure has\Ngreat presence!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You could even\Nsay he's imposing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:49.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't make any\Nreal mistakes, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.46,0:07:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can tell how grueling\Nhis practice sessions must be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.21,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't look it, but he's a\Ndiligent player, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.03,0:07:59.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though his mentor,\NTakayanagi-kun is so shallow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:08:01.22,Sign,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Name of mentor: Akira Takayanagi
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.68,0:08:04.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,First place in all of his recent competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.68,0:08:07.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's certainly flying high at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He's a phenom ready to\Ntake the world by storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.57,0:08:12.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In comparison,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.46,0:08:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,she's fallen quite far back in the pack.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.86,0:08:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Man, she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.53,0:08:25.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.99,0:08:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.04,0:08:31.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's Igawa-san.\NShe's popular, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:35.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I knew they seemed familiar.\NWhen I used to go cheer Kousei on,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.67,0:08:38.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,both that Aiza-kun,\Nand Igawa-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.55,0:08:42.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I used to see those\Nthree together all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.30,0:08:45.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I remember because their\Nnames were always at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:48.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But of course, it was Kousei\Nwho always ended up in first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.97,0:08:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, and why are\Nyou acting so smug again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.14,0:08:54.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So listen, is this Emi-chan\Nany good at the piano?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.77,0:08:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's got to be good.\NBecause she's cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.02,0:08:58.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know how to size up people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.44,0:09:01.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I bet Emi-chan's gonna\Nrun away with this competition.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:02.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, 'cause she's so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.57,0:09:04.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Already using her first name?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.05,0:09:05.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jerk...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.49,0:09:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, but I think Igawa-san's\Nbeen struggling a little lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.29,0:09:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An honorable mention at\Nthe Kumagai Competition,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,third place at the\NTanizaki Music Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.00,0:09:18.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and the other day, she didn't even\Nmake it past the preliminaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.34,0:09:22.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like she's been\Nrunning hot and cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.88,0:09:25.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To think that those three always\Nused to be a lock for the Top 3...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.51,0:09:28.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.47,0:09:31.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.18,0:09:32.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Takayanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hello, Ms. Ochiai.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.19,0:09:36.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.40,0:09:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How's it going with\Nyour student, Igawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:41.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a snide man.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.24,0:09:45.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aiza-kun's performance was masterful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it's all\Ndue to your instruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.07,0:09:50.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well... thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.24,0:09:52.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In my case, the student\Nhas surpassed the master!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.62,0:09:59.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I do believe it's time for\Nhim to start thinking globally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.46,0:10:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Since there probably isn't anything\Nleft for him to accomplish domestically.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:06.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can challenge\Nhim anymore in Japan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.68,0:10:08.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You saw that yourself, didn't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.05,0:10:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In everyone's eyes, Takeshi is No. 1!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, he'll destroy Arima,\Nand head overseas!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.10,0:10:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Feel free.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:20.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So how's she doing? Igawa-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.86,0:10:23.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... Emi can be\Nso temperamental, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.65,0:10:27.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The most trivial thing can have\Na drastic effect on her performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like her new shoes pinching her toes,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.62,0:10:34.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,or her neighbor humming in a bizarre way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She can even be swayed\Nby the weather that day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.67,0:10:40.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For the last two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.21,0:10:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,it's been so hectic for everyone,\Ntrying to keep her motivated...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.13,0:10:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because the goal she should\Nhave vanquished had disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.39,0:10:51.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But... it's different today.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.35,0:10:56.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The last two years...\NThe goal she should have vanquished...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.40,0:11:00.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The goal she should have vanquished!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.83,0:11:15.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you implying that she\Ndoesn't see Takeshi as her goal?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.37,0:11:18.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Aiza-kun doesn't see\N Emi as a rival either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"The results speak for themselves..."\NIt's written all over your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to pick a\Nfight with me, Ms. Ochiai?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.68,0:11:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who threw\Ndown the gauntlet, Mr. Takayanagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.02,0:11:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We women are combative\Ncreatures. Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.61,0:11:44.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.65,0:11:51.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We will now resume judging.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:56.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aiza-kun's reign will end today.\NEmi will bring an end to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh, goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.14,0:12:15.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's turning red!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.14,0:12:22.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been a while\Nsince I felt this way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.57,0:12:33.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.33,0:12:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been two years.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.67,0:12:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was five,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:50.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I went to a piano recital\Nto cheer on a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.55,0:12:56.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just when I was about to\Nfall asleep from boredom,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.89,0:12:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He appeared onstage.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was such a\Nbundle of nerves,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.53,0:13:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my heart started pounding.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.90,0:13:14.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That Arima-kun was? Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found out later that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.99,0:13:21.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,that was the first time he'd ever\Nperformed in front of other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.42,0:13:34.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That moment of silence before\Nhis fingers touched the keys...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.51,0:13:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The time he took to bid his\Nhesitation and confusion farewell...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.14,0:13:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The moment his fingers touched the keys,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.35,0:13:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,my future was decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:55.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! Oops!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.21,0:14:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What, you started bawling?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.42,0:14:12.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Embarrassing, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.96,0:14:15.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it was awkward for young Arima!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.47,0:14:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He was crestfallen, and\Nbeat it out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.85,0:14:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My heart wouldn't stop pounding,\Nand tears were filling my eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.35,0:14:26.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All of my emotions came\Ngushing out at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.73,0:14:30.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was just so moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.61,0:14:35.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As if I was embodying all\Nthe pleasure music brings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.49,0:14:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But he, on the other hand...\NKousei Arima changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.08,0:14:43.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like a machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,His mother's puppet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.64,0:14:45.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A slave to the sheet music.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.62,0:14:47.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A pianist made only for competitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.29,0:14:53.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Kousei Arima's mother,\NSaki Arima, was dreaming.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.63,0:14:57.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can understand that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.51,0:14:59.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She entered her son in\Nthat competition to test him,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.93,0:15:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and her dreams for him began\Nwith his magnificent performance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.06,0:15:06.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The dreams that she could\Nnever realize for herself.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.48,0:15:09.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And so she drilled him...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.73,0:15:12.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}to give performances that would leave\Nresults, that could win competitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Exactly what the score\Ncalls for. Like a machine.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.91,0:15:20.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I get it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:24.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As an instructor, it's painful\Nnot to be able to deny that.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.08,0:15:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But you're different, aren't you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.96,0:15:31.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you're a strong child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:43.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You know, she can be unfriendly, and\Nshe says stuff that sounds pretty mean,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.43,0:15:47.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,but she really has a thing\Nfor you, you know, Arima.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.10,0:15:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.35,0:15:51.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I swear, it's like\Nshe's in love with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.56,0:15:54.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, she was always telling me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:58.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Takeshi, you don't know\Nthe real Arima, do you?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.25,0:16:18.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So beautiful...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.05,0:16:19.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.88,0:16:25.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She just takes my breath away.\NHer, and the black piano...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:28.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I mean, really... what a sight!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:54.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a lovely sound. But...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:56.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If that's all she's got...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.66,0:17:30.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that Emi can be erratic.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.37,0:17:32.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like a stormy sea,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the waves of her emotions\Nare surging unsteadily.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.42,0:17:37.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That being the case - today...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.96,0:17:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It wouldn't be a surprise to see\Nthose waves reach their crest.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm in sync with the piano.\NMy fingers feel light.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.01,0:17:52.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today, I'm in the zone. It's probably...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.31,0:17:54.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...because the scone I had\Nfor breakfast was so good.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.23,0:18:00.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because my new dress looks good on me.\N Because I'm having a good hair day.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.82,0:18:02.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's got to be it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.53,0:18:05.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, of course that's not it!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.28,0:18:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not a child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.62,0:18:09.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So why am I making\Nexcuses to myself?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.04,0:18:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's here. After two\Nyears, he's so near...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.71,0:18:18.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's gotten taller. He looks\Na little more mature.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.04,0:18:21.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I knew him at a glance.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.00,0:18:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ever since that moment, my\Nexcitement has been surging.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.72,0:18:26.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He's right there, and he's watching me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.34,0:18:27.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you feel that way, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.10,0:18:32.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Don't make me laugh. Because I...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.06,0:18:36.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've been playing the piano all this\Ntime in order to reject Kousei Arima.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.90,0:18:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know that she has the technique.\N But not at this level...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.73,0:18:45.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Go! Emi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.03,0:18:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it all out with a bang!\NLet your feelings reach them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.28,0:18:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A fourteen-year-old girl\Nhas this audience enthralled.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.04,0:18:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is she really a\Njunior high student?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.33,0:18:59.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to reject you.\N Even if I lose,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:03.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}even if I get trounced, I'm going\Nto reject you every time.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Playing for competitions...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.30,0:19:08.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's not the Kousei Arima\Nthat I want to hear.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.22,0:19:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm going to reject\Nyou with my playing.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.76,0:19:14.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What I want to hear is...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.02,0:19:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red, yellow, yellow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.61,0:19:23.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Are these her emotions?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.03,0:19:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red and yellow...\NAnger and...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.92,0:19:40.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you feel that way, too?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.42,0:19:42.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, I do.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm only here because of you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.80,0:19:48.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just under four minutes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:51.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A performance lasting\Njust under four minutes...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.55,0:19:53.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what made me a pianist.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come back, come back,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.52,0:20:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the Kousei Arima that I looked up to!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.35,0:20:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring! Let it ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.40,0:20:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:04.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My piano!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:07.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring! Let it ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.40,0:20:09.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.74,0:20:12.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.66,0:20:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Red and yellow. Her anger,\Nand... Her loneliness.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.96,0:20:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Chopin's Étude,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.79,0:20:24.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Op. 25, No. 11.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.63,0:20:28.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Le vent d'hiver" - Winter Wind.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.83,0:20:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Super-cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:20:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dial it down, Watari!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.08,0:21:06.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right... So you play by pouring your\Nsoul into the notes, too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.84,0:21:09.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.67,0:21:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let it ring.{\i0}
